Text: 'A story of a married woman with her two growing sons, a lazy husband who lives
  mostly on the rental income and a I''ll mother in-law. This woman wishing to see
  the world but stuck in the family life taking care cocking teaching school students
  to earn extra money..  Her world is the four walls of the house , rarely stepping
  outside of her home saving bit by bit,  but every time she saves a tragedy awaits
  health bills,  pending loans, children collage fees. Will she even travel  to her
  dream destination? #'
